title: War of the Roses: He Suddenly Wants to Walk the Dog All the Time
description: Julie has a friend they have a nickname for because she has big fake boobs.  Her and her husband ran into that friend at the dog park and all of a sudden her husband wants to walk the dog all the time.  She also saw some things he purchased on the Target app that don't add up.  Is he walking the dog to get more steps in or does he have an ulterior motive?
